Package org.apache.click.servlet

Class MockSession

java.lang.Object
org.apache.click.servlet.MockSession
All Implemented Interfaces:
HttpSession
public class MockSession extends Object implements HttpSession
Mock implementation of HttpSession.

Implements all of the methods from the standard HttpSession class plus helper methods to aid setting up a session.
